        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for copy of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> in name of Anthropologische Gesellschaft, Munich.</p> 
            <p>Dr Born has demonstrated that all Batrachia and their relatives the Anura have six toes.</p> 
<p>Sends short paper on intelligence of cephalopods ["Die Cephalopoden in der zoologischen Station des Dr Dohrn", <hi rend="italic">Z. Wiss. Zool.</hi> 26 (1876): 1–23].</p> 
        </abstract>
